    <section>


        <div class="jumbotron">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Meet Mailman <i class="fa fa-envelope-o"></i></h2>
                <p>
                    Reward timely replies with Bitcoin, and filter spam with the Blockchain!
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="container">
            <!-- Stack the columns on mobile by making one full-width and the other half-width -->
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
                    <div class="well">
                        <p>
                            Dear Alpha Tester
                            <br /> Welcome to Mailman. This web app was written in Pakistan, using Node.js, the code is hosted on Github and deployed on Heroku. If you'd like access to the code,
                            <a href="https://twitter.com/home?status=@amingilani hey, I'd like to review the source for mailman">
                          tweet for it.</a>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Mailman has primary functions:
                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    Reward replies: <br />
                                    Automatically notify and deliver
                                    rewards to recepients if they reply within
                                    48 hours of your email. <strong>Otherwise you get
                                    your money back.</strong>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    Fight spam: <br />
                                    Issue users a custom "@mailman.ninja"
                                    email address which charges 200 bits to
                                    deliver the email. <strongs>You recieve the
                                    fee.</strongs>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
                    <div class="well message-mail">
                      <p>
                        Documentation: <br />
                        <ol>
                          <li>
                            Rewarding replies:
                            <ol>
                              <li>
                                Include CC: Mailman &lt;mailman@mailman.ninja&gt; in your email.
                              </li>
                              <li>
                                Pay invoice to the BTC address mailman issues.
                              </li>
                              <li>
                                Wait for the reply, mailman will handle the rest. <br />
                                If you don't get a reply within 48 hours, Mailman
                                will send you your money back.
                              </li>
                            </ol>
                          </li>
                          <li>
                            Charge for delivery: //=&gt; <strong>Coming soon</strong>
                            <ol>
                              <li>
                                Sign up for Mailman. Recieve your custom email address.
                              </li>
                              <li>
                                Use your new email address in places where you expect
                                spambots to harvest it.<br />
                                <pre>$ git config --global user.email "john@mailman.ninja"</pre>
                              </li>
                              <li>
                                Wait for people to email you, Mailman will handle the rest.
                              </li>
                            </ol>
                          </li>
                        </ol>
                      </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

