                    Found a bug? Report it. <a href="https://github.com/mailmanhq/mailman/issues/new"><i class="fa fa-github"></i> Github</a> or <a href="mailto:bugs@mailman.ninja"><i class="fa fa-envelope-o"></i> Email</a>
